parameters:
\N<Man>Hey, hey, is that really true...? Can't believe even that
guy is joining the training soldiers' assembly.

\N<Man>Yeah, seems like he was transferred to this town late last
night.

\N<Man>Ahh, I hate it, I hate it. I definitely don't want to be
matched up with someone like that...

\N<Segi>Miss Irime, what happened? What's all this commotion
about...?

\N<Irime>Oh, apparently a famous death row inmate has been
transferred to our town.

\N<Irime>I've heard about him. Murder, robbery, rape, he's the worst
kind of scumbag who does it all.

\N<Irime>Zozoye... that's right, no mistake, it's this guy. Why do
you have such information...

\N<Irime>W-wait a minute, please. Don't tell me this guy is your next
opponent...!?

\N<Irime>...You shouldn't make such a face. You've managed to get by
until now. That's right, I'm sure this time too, if it's
you...

\N<Man>...I'd rather avoid any quarrels. All I can do is to live
quietly, making sure that no trouble comes my way.

\N<Woman>Once the training assembly is over, those people from Ryuda
will leave this town, won't they? That's okay to think,
right?
\N<Segi>...I have to go to the management office.
\N<Segi>...Let's send Riia to the training grounds.
\N<Segi>...I have to go to the management office.
\N<Segi>...Let's send Riia to the training grounds.
\N<Segi>...Irime-san, what on earth are you thinking...
\N<Riia>Rame-chan... and Fubii and that child too.

\N<Riia>I wonder where everyone is going after sneaking out of the
training grounds...
\N<Riia>Rame-chan... and Fubii and that kid too.

\N<Riia>I wonder where everyone is going after sneaking out of the
training grounds...
\N<Segi>What are you all doing at this hour?

\N<Fubii>Good evening, ma'am. What else would we be doing? We were
studying at the training grounds.

\N<Segi>Even if that's true, it's outrageous to keep a girl out at
this time of night.

\N<Fubii>That's a harsh way to put it. She's here of her own free
will, right?

\N<Fubii>Ahaha, are you satisfied now? We're off to have a study
session at my place, so we'll be going now, okay?

\N<Segi>Irime-san... Why again with Zuuteruka... I don't
understand... but...
\N<Segi>...Irime-san, what on earth are you thinking...
\N<Segi>...Irime-san, what on earth are you thinking...
\N<Segi>...The arena is in the opposite direction.
